{"type": "article", "id": 38460, "title": "这个腕表里，藏着水泥做的时间台阶｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-05T23:07:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 36763, "name": "DOIY"}, {"id": 38240, "name": "22 Design Studio"}, {"id": 38241, "name": "Stitch Design"}, {"id": 38242, "name": "ipnot"}, {"id": 38243, "name": "Christoffer Relander"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 229, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170305224952GXeapjcflsy72Zvw.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>四度空间机械表 by 22 Design Studio</h3><p>水泥制作的时钟似乎并不稀奇，那么腕表的表面呢？以水泥制品见长的台湾 <a href=\"http://www.22designstudio.com.tw/\">22 Design Studio</a> 曾在两年前推出过一套以“四度空间”为概念打造的水泥腕表，最近设计团队又带来了它的迭代款。这些机械表的表面延续了标志性的旋转阶梯造型，经过两年的研发，他们在维持强度的同时，成功将阶梯的单层厚度降低到仅有 0.3 毫米。除此之外，表面还留有一个日期窗口，刚好还能窥探到一部分机芯的结构。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/fourthdimensionmechanicalwatch\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 18800 新台币起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703052250408oNHJDWTmnQU1MFa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225040c6XKd42TRurwMIY1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703052250403xymA48QYkjBqZCG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225040tCsHEdAD5owbnqux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225040nQa2YXWEz9PyldIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>100 things by DOIY</h3><p>人生只有一次，你愿意挑战“一百件必须在死前完成的事”吗？由西班牙创意品牌 DOIY 设计的 100 things 可以被视为海报版本的 to do list，每当你完成一件就可以将第一层的文字版剥开，露出底部的图像，过程就好像是集邮一样。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://doiydesign.com/product/poster-100-things-must-do/\">链接</a>购买，售价为 29.95 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703052251040iEPWTSdmv4tBYGn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225103OWACpoTydKLZwB1s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225103plVWh4o0x7NDLUJP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225103ofUSV291FjywDTtm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Baking Cat by Amy Tsang</h3><p>The Baking Cat 是一个由加拿大艺术系学生 Amy Tsang 创立的手工陶器品牌。在过去两年的时间里，Tsang 以自己的爱猫 Soya 为灵感制作了一系列温润可爱的猫咪马克杯和小花盆，它们的颜色大多以黑白为主，不会给人太过花哨的感觉。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/uk/shop/TheBakingCat\">链接</a>购买，售价从 21.54 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225435v26iHVOqjsFIPKYU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703052254354XAkNPlgvq6DGnmH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225435rpQx36kVAX91gy0W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225436eTsVFHxDmrM7A4qh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Embroidered miniature objects by ipnot</h3><p>自从发现了祖母留下的刺绣，日本艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.ipnot.info/\">ipnot</a> 就为法式花芯结（French knot）所吸引，并尝试用一针一线打造出一个毛茸茸的迷你世界：拉面、番茄、寿司，甚至是一碗抹茶都不在话下。如果你喜欢她的创作，还可以关注她的&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ipnot\">Twitter</a> 和 <a href=\"https://instagram.com/ipnot\">Instagram</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225143bQTnh3tFDSaM074Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703052251446pVDms8rTxOgzea5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703052251430NuvI2OLkyslhoqV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225144rF9yg0xPOZhHmu1X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225144aRfDWENvK7SoTcpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jarred &amp; Displaced by Christoffer Relander</h3><p>怀着对家乡的思念，芬兰摄影师 <a href=\"http://www.christofferrelander.com/\">Christoffer Relander</a> 历时一年半时间在当地的乡间进行拍摄，随后将这些作品制成了一套名为 <a href=\"http://www.christofferrelander.com/projects/jarred-displaced/\">Jarred &amp; Displaced</a> 的瓶中风景。在处理照片时，Relander 并没有使用 Photoshop，而是通过双重曝光将记忆里的景色巧妙地“装”进一个个玻璃罐头当中。如果你对拍摄过程感兴趣的话，还可以通过<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/191142013\">链接</a>观看一段幕后花絮。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225232VI13TEKvSod9uq6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225232ai8tcJGRTKdpD05k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225232oZkypCJOb4q1Mert.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225233s64d2HLGDScQoXlm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.167000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Palermo by Stitch Design Co.</h3><p>Palermo 是一个来自美国的护肤品品牌，所有产品都选用天然材料手工制成，娇小玲珑的体积也是它的一大特色。为了突出这种轻质感，负责包装设计的 <a href=\"http://stitchdesignco.com/\">Stitch Design Co.</a> 将配色相当温和的三角形色块零散地分布在纸盒上，看起来简单清爽。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225302V4n8rxDTm6EjAkQu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225303R3Nd8xGLMr1tJDTW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225302W9zRC4Um6hx7LFo3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170305225302vY2V9JUEiSxHRGyI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}